ZH: 每逢寒假，我都会回家和家人团聚。
EN: Every winter vacation, I go home to reunite with my family.

ZH: 每逢春节，我们家都会举办一场盛大的晚宴。
EN: Every Chinese New Year, our family hosts a grand banquet.

ZH: 每逢年底，我们公司都会举行一次年会。
EN: Every year-end, our company holds an annual meeting.

ZH: 每逢周末，我总是喜欢和朋友们一起去郊游。
EN: Every weekend, I always enjoy going on outings with my friends.

ZH: 每逢下雨天，我都会带上雨伞。
EN: Every rainy day, I always bring an umbrella with me.

ZH: 每逢暑假，我们家常常去海边度假。
EN: Every summer vacation, our family often goes on seaside holidays.

ZH: 每逢生日，我都会送一份特别的礼物给我的朋友。
EN: Every birthday, I always give a special gift to my friend.

ZH: 每逢重要的考试，我都会提前复习。
EN: Every important exam, I always start revising in advance.

ZH: 每逢周五晚上，我们都会去看电影。
EN: Every Friday evening, we go watch a movie.

ZH: 每逢假期，城市里的旅游景点都特别拥挤。
EN: Every holiday, tourist attractions in the city are always crowded.

ZH: 每逢冬天，我总是喜欢喝一杯热腾腾的咖啡。
EN: Every winter, I always enjoy drinking a hot cup of coffee.

ZH: 每逢夏季，我都会变得非常懒惰。
EN: Every summer, I become very lazy.

ZH: 每逢晴天，我都会在户外散步。
EN: Every sunny day, I go for a walk outdoors.

ZH: 每逢阴天，我总是感到有点郁闷。
EN: Every cloudy day, I always feel a bit gloomy.

ZH: 每逢他生气时，我都会小心翼翼地说话。
EN: Every time he gets angry, I speak very cautiously.

ZH: 每逢热闹的节日，我们都会在家里摆酒席招待亲朋好友。
EN: Every festive holiday, we host a banquet at home to entertain relatives and friends.

ZH: 每逢大雪纷飞的日子，我总是想起童年的欢乐。
EN: Every day when heavy snow falls, I always think of the joy of childhood.

ZH: 每逢见到你的笑容，我的心情都会变得愉快起来。
EN: Every time I see your smile, my mood becomes joyful.

ZH: 每逢考试结束，我都会感到松了一口气。
EN: Every time exams are over, I feel relieved.

ZH: 每逢他来信，我总是兴奋地打开阅读。
EN: Every time I receive a letter from him, I eagerly open and read it.
